                           DEMO

There is a freely distributable demo version of Origins available, which
has a limit on the number of records, has some printing functions
disabled, and does not include the GEDCOM utilities.  The demo can be
found on BIX and CIS, and the demo file Origins.lzh (and Origins.readme)
are available for anonymous ftp at wuarchive.wustl.edu (128.252.135.4) in
the directory /systems/amiga/demos/commercial.

